screen_desc: A pop-up message on a mobile app screen asks, "Log out of your account?" with two options: "CANCEL" and "LOG OUT." The background shows various menu options such as "Memories," "Saved," "Groups," "Video," "Help & support," "Settings & privacy," and "Also from Meta." The time displayed at the top of the screen is 8:50, and the device is connected to 4G with full signal strength and battery.
